                            "course-unit-quotes": "",
                            "course-unit-case-study": "<h5>A construction material company is introducing a new environmentally friendly paint to the market. To develop a marketing plan, the marketing manager identifies two key target segments that they need to reach, the developers who are building and the consultants that recommend and approve quality.</h5>\r\n<h5>Here is how their marketing campaign looks like:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Target Audience: a) Developers b) Consultants</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Value Proposition: a) Saves Money b) In line with green standards</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h5>Call for Action: a) Buy now and get 15% off b) download the whitepaper</h5>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>",
